WITH log as (
                        INSERT INTO task_log(task_id,
                                             warehouse_id,
                                             queue_name,
                                             task_data,
                                             status,
                                             entity_id,
                                             entity_type,
                                             attempt,
                                             started_at,
                                             duration)
                        SELECT task_id,
                               warehouse_id,
                               queue_name,
                               task_data,
                               $2,
                               entity_id,
                               entity_type,
                               attempt,
                               picked_up_at,
                               case when picked_up_at is not null
                                   then now() - picked_up_at
                               end
                        FROM task
                        WHERE (status = $3 OR $6) AND task_id = ANY($1) AND (queue_name = $4 OR $5)
                    )
                    DELETE FROM task
                    WHERE (status = $3 OR $6) AND (queue_name = $4 OR $5)
                    AND task_id = ANY($1)
